[[category:Balanced Annihilation]] Missile Towers are light defense structures made for destroying aircraft. Their advantages over an [[LLT]] are that they have a longer range and do not consume energy, and are homing. However, they have much less health and do not shoot as quickly, so they should not be used as your main defensive structure.
