}}


===flankingBonus===
{{tag
|name = defaultMode
|type = int
|default = 1
|description = The default {{xtaglink|Gamedev:UnitDefs|flankingBonusMode}} for units. Can be <code>0</code> - No flanking bonus. Mode <code>1</code> builds up the ability to move over time, and swings to face attacks, but does not respect the way the unit is facing. Mode <code>2</code> also can swing, but moves with the unit as it turns. Mode <code>3</code> stays with the unit as it turns and otherwise doesn't move, the ideal mode to simulate something such as tank armour. 
}}


===los===
