== minimal functional startscript ==
Based on {{forumlink|topic=32893&p=566971#p566953|title=these two posts:}} 
<pre>
[GAME]
{
	MapName=DeltaSiegeDry;
	GameType=Balanced Annihilation V8.10;
	IsHost=1;
	[PLAYER0]
	{
		Team=0;
	}
	[TEAM0]
	{
		TeamLeader=0;
		AllyTeam=0;
	}
	[ALLYTEAM0]
	{
	}
}
</pre>


